KABOKWENI – Linco Believe Makhubela, was arrested on Sunday, at his hideout in Sabie, following an investigation  by police after the disappearance of , Nokubonga Nonyane. Nokubonga was last seen while playing with her peers on Friday, at Mahushu.  Her lifeless body was found dumped in a ditch, on Monday morning. Makhubela was remanded in custody until July 27 , pending further investigation.